</div></div><div class="sqs-block spacer-block sqs-block-spacer sized vsize-1" data-block-type="21" id="block-yui_3_17_2_1_1722514477920_27390"><div class="sqs-block-content">&nbsp;</div></div><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" data-border-radii="&#123;&quot;topLeft&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;,&quot;topRight&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;,&quot;bottomLeft&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;,&quot;bottomRight&quot;:&#123;&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;value&quot;:0.0&#125;&#125;" id="block-cac757ea9124e103b0c0"><div class="sqs-block-content">

<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <h3 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;">What’s included? </h3><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">Venue rental for up to 20 guests on a Wednesday or Thursday</p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">4 Hour Rental (to include 2 event hours)</p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">2 outdoor ceremony options (Indoor rain plan available)</p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">All Tables, Chairs, Linens</p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">Décor + Faux Floral (bouquet, corsages, Boutonnieres, floral sprays for gazebo)&nbsp;</p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">Event staff to handle bartending, set up/breakdown and coordination (beer/wine/champagne only to be provided by couple)</p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">Indoor and outdoor Music + Microphone </p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class=""><strong><em>4 hour rental is from start to finish at venue and includes time to rehearse, get dressed, photography, ceremony and food/drink service</em></strong></p><p class="" data-rte-preserve-empty="true" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"></p><h3 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;">Other notes about elopements:</h3><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">Dressing rooms are available to change on-site. Hair and make-up must be completed off-site. </p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">Just bring: Lite snacks, alcohol (beer/wine/champagne only), finishing touches, officiant, and photographer! </p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class="">This package is not suitable for couples wanting a dinner or meal. The timeline allows for light snacks or appetizers only. If you would like a meal at your mini-reception, see our micro wedding packages above.</p><p style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;" class=""><em>Reference our </em><a href="https://brine-red-ridge-receptions.squarespace.com/preferred-vendors-and-lodging"><span style="text-decoration:underline"><em>preferred vendor list</em></span></a><em> for affordable food and cake options!</em></p><p class="" data-rte-preserve-empty="true" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"></p><h3 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;"><a href="https://redridgereceptions.com/contact" target="">Reserve Your Date</a></h3>
</div>

























