      <section id="micro-wedding-elopement-packages-austin-faq" class="Index-page"  data-collection-id="66ab810081e60d77aa5fc4cd" data-parallax-id="66ab810081e60d77aa5fc4cd" data-edit-main-image="Background">

        <div class="Index-page-content ">
          <div class="sqs-layout sqs-grid-12 columns-12" data-type="page" data-updated-on="1722902340557" id="page-66ab810081e60d77aa5fc4cd"><div class="row sqs-row"><div class="col sqs-col-12 span-12"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-cfc49689445dc6ea1987"><div class="sqs-block-content">

<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <h2 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;">Micro Wedding and Elopement Package FAQ</h2>
</div>

























</div></div></div></div><div class="row sqs-row"><div class="col sqs-col-6 span-6"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-6dada1bc013253fd6027"><div class="sqs-block-content">

<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>Can I add more people to my package?<br></strong><br>You may add up to an additional 10 people for $500, not to exceed 30 for mini or 40 for micro.<br><br><br><strong>Can I add more time to my package?<br></strong><br>Additional getting ready time is available for $150 per hour.&nbsp;</p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">We are not able to add any additional event hours to these packages. If you’re interested in a longer rental time, check out our <a href="https://redridgereceptions.com/all-inclusive-wedding-packages-austin"><span style="text-decoration:underline">weekend all-inclusive packages</span></a>.<br><br><br><strong>What hours are available for my event?</strong></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">You are allotted a 4 hour rental for the elopement or 6 hour rental for a micro-wedding package. All weekday events end by 8pm.<br><br><br><strong>How far in advance should I book my date?<br></strong><br>We allow bookings for mini and micro weddings up to 1 year in advance! Our experienced team is able to help you plan in just a few short weeks, though, if you’re on a tight timeline!<br><br><br><strong>What payment options are available?<br></strong><br>Option 1: 3 payments due at booking, 6 months before event and 1 month before event<br><br>Option 2: half down; half due 30 days before your event<br><br><br><strong>What are your vendor and catering requirements?</strong></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">You’re welcome to use any photographer and officiant of your choice! You may bring in store bought, pre-packaged appetizer platters or snacks.&nbsp;</p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">For a micro-wedding with dinner buffet, an approved caterer must be hired. Please see our preferred list. </p>
</div>

























</div></div></div><div class="col sqs-col-6 span-6"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-47adfa0997d495245896"><div class="sqs-block-content">

<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>How much coordination is provided by Red Ridge?</strong></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">When you book with us, we’ll give you access to a personal planning portal with forms specific to micro and mini weddings!&nbsp; The forms include: floorplan, timeline, processional, music, vendor list, bar menu, and décor selections. <br><br>We’re available to help answer questions as you go through these forms. After your forms are complete, we put together a production schedule and let you go through it and make any edits before the big day. We send this to your vendors and confirm the timeline with them, as well. <br><br>On the wedding day, our team handles all set up/breakdown and manages the timeline. We want you to be able to truly relax and enjoy your day! Bonus: Your wedding party and family also gets to relax while our team handles the details! <br><br><br><strong>Do I get to pick out my own music?</strong></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">We want to play the music YOU want to hear! We provide a music survey online where you can let us know all of your song selections for your ceremony, special dances, cake cutting, etc… There are tons of suggestions on the form and you’re also able to give us a must play and do not play list. <br><br><br><strong>Can I bring in my own decorations?</strong></p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">We have lots of in-house décor and faux floral that you’re welcome to use. You can absolutely bring in your own decorations and finishing touches! Our team does a full set up and breakdown of everything on the wedding day and we even pack up and load all of your décor, gifts and leftover food and alcohol at the end of the event. DIY floral must be pre-assembled beforehand.  <br><br><br><strong>Can I schedule a rehearsal before my wedding date?</strong> <br><br>For micro and mini weddings, we only offer a same day rehearsal and this is included in your rental time. The rehearsal generally takes about 20 minutes with a small wedding party. If you do not plan to see each other before the ceremony, that’s no problem! We generally do a run through with the bride + wedding party and a separate run through with the groom.</p><p class="" data-rte-preserve-empty="true" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"></p>
</div>

























</div></div></div></div><div class="row sqs-row"><div class="col sqs-col-12 span-12"><div class="sqs-block button-block sqs-block-button" data-block-type="53" id="block-yui_3_17_2_1_1722515874316_70732"><div class="sqs-block-content">

